I’ve been going back & forth about what’s next for me in my life & I got distracted by what I think is best for me vs what got me to where I am now & that’s listening to that voice in your head (God) .. I felt like when my lease was up I should move out of state and start over, but nothing was falling into place like I needed it to & I decided it wasn’t the right time so I gave myself a timeline & ima do everything I need to do to make sure I do things the RIGHT way & the way God is telling me to 💯🤝🏾

I’m making this post to tell anybody who is battling with trusting yourself or facing a hard decision, just pray about it & LISTEN to that voice in your head .. it’s there for a reason 🫶🏾

BREAKTHROUGH all the blockades
BREAKTHROUGH all the doubt
BREAKTHROUGH all the distractions 

Lock in on your future & what God has in store for you❗️🔥🗣️

- Groovy 🌊🏄🏾‍♂️💙
